{"tid":100950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前面個細佬仔真係好撚型","createTime":"2017-01-30T12:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T12:47:43.000Z","uid":21958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"449861f326f091664faee7861e03559bd92d70cf","tid":100950,"uid":21958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"頭先搭巴士前面有個細佬仔睇落8-10歲左右<br />\n一路都同緊佢屋企人傾緊計<br />\n<br />\n講講下個細佬冇啦啦話：咦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老豆呢件衫係Made in China嘅！<br />\n跟住佢執邊個個Auntie即刻話：車！你夠係Made in China啦<br />\n個細佬仔諗都冇諗即刻答佢話：No！我係Made in Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個Auntie又話：你錯啦你係Made in China<br />\n<br />\n到最尾個細佬仔強調左好多次自己係Made in Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又西哂面咁望住個Auntie話I am not from China 個女人先收左聲<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772cfe2a01c71133af843a7c0310ad0063756760","tid":100950,"uid":45459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個細路仔成1米8幾 又高又型 <br />\n出哂水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f30ca587ff21b3e380412d4e227bd329a08793","tid":100950,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"I am not from China ！ 我型唔型？"}]}